ama Abeykoon\n|\n|-\n|1973\n|281\n|''Hondata Hondai''\n|Chammi\n|\n|-\n|1974\n|282\n|''[[Ahas Gauwa]]''\n|Post office co-worker\n|\n|-\n|1974\n|285\n|''Kasthuri Suwanda''\n|Kanchana\n|\n|-\n|1974\n|294\n|''Susee''\n|Susee\n|\n|-\n|1974\n|299\n|''Senakeliya''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1975\n|311\n|''Awa Soya Adare''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1975\n|313\n|''Kohoma Kiyannada''\n|Samanthi\n|\n|-\n|1975\n|\n|''Sooraya Soorayamai''\n|Nilanthi / Mango 'Nanda'\n|\n|-\n|1975\n|327\n|''Sadhana''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1975\n|330\n|''Sangeetha''\n|Sangeetha / Geetha (two births)\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sarasaviya.lk/features/2019/11/28/12689/\u0d94\u0db6\u0dd9-\u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db4-\u0db8\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0dc3\u0dad\u0dd4\u0da7\u0dba\u0dd2 |title=All about Sangeetha |publisher=Sarasaviya |accessdate=23 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|1975\n|\n|''Nayana''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|332\n|''Pradeepaya Maa Wewa''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|335\n|''Kawda Raja''\n|Chintha\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|\n|''Yaar Aval'' (Tamil Film)\n|\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|336\n|''Wasana''\n|Sudarshi Rajadasa\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|337\n|''Ganga''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|342\n|''Diyamanthi''\n|Chitra Saparamandu\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|348\n|''Unnath Dahai Malath Dahai''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|351\n|''Onna Mame Kella Panapi''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|252\n|''Saradiyelge Putha''\n|Subha\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|356\n|''Adarei Man Adarei''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1976\n|383\n|''Zashis (Rahas Kumanthranaya)''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1977\n|359\n|''Neela''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1977\n|360\n|''Sakunthala''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1977\n|365\n|''Hithuwoth Hithuwamai''\n|Apsara\n|\n|-\n|1977\n|367\n|''Pembara Madhu''\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/070211/TV/004tv.html |title=Rupavahini shows \u2018Pembara Madu\u2019 |publisher=Sunday Times |accessdate=10 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|1977\n|368\n|''Deviyani Oba Kohida''\n|\n|\n|-\n|1977\n|369\n|''[[How to Be an Adult|Eya Dan Loku Lamayek]]''\n|Katuwalagedera 'Susila' Susilawathie 'Susee'\n|\n|-\n|1977\n|376\n|''Siripala Saha Ranmenika''\n|Ranmanika\n|\n|-\n|1978\n|\n|''[[Pilot Premnath|Pilot P