ron\n|\n|-\n|\n|\n|''Udu Sulanga''\n|\n|\n|-\n|\n|\n|''Prathiravaya''\n|\n|\n|-\n|\n|\n|''Muthuetaye Modayo''\n|\n|\n|-\n|\n|\n|''Bhavatharana''\n|\n|\n|-\n|\n|\n|''Ayu''\n|\n|\n|-\n|TBD\n|\n|''[[Rookada Panchi]]''\n|Cameo appearance.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/181202/magazine/a-cinematic-carnival-by-the-sea-322368.html |title=A cinematic carnival by the sea |publisher=Sunday Times|accessdate=17 January 2019}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|TBD\n|\n|''Monara Vilak''\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sarasaviya.lk/films-local/2019/08/22/8462/\u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc5\u0ddc\u0dc3\u0dca-\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0da7-\u0db4\u0dc3\u0dd4-\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd3-\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dad\u0dca-\u0dba\u0dc5\u0dd2-\u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca-\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1-\u201c\u0db8\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u201d |title=Malini with Sanath after 14 years |publisher=Sarasaviya|accessdate=22 August 2019}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==Director and actor==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Film\n! Note\n|-\n|1984\n|''Sasara Chethana''\n| Also as Producer \n|-\n|1987\n|''Ahinsa''\n| Also as Producer \n|-\n|1991\n|''Sthree''\n|  \n|-\n|1994\n|''Sanda Madala''\n| Also as Script writer \n|}\n\n{{s-start}} {{s-ach|aw}}\n{{s-bef|before=Swarna Kahavita <br> for ''Binaramalee'' |years=1970}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Sarasaviya Best Actress Award]] <br> for ''Hingana Kolle''|years=1980}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Vasanthi Chathurani]] <br> for [[Ganga Addara]]|years=1981}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Vasanthi Chathurani]] <br> for [[Ganga Addara]]|years=1981}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Sarasaviya Best Actress Award]] <br> for ''Aradhana''|years=1982}}\n{{s-aft|after=<br> for}} \n|-\n{{s-bef|before=<br> for}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Most Popular Actress Award <br> for |years=1980}}\n{{s-aft|after=<br> for}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=<br> for}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Most Popular Actress Award <br> for |years=1981}}\n{{s-aft|after=<br> for}}\n{{end}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*[http://www.nfc.gov.lk/artist/m